OL,5, Two of P&O Ferries' competitors are set
OL,6, to meet officials from the Department  
OL,7, for Transport to discuss the fallout   
OL,8, from P&O's decision to sack 800 staff. 
OL,10,FBosses from DFDS and Stena Lines have  
OL,11,Fbeen invited for talks on Monday as the
OL,12,Fgovernment plans to force ferries to   
OL,13,Fpay the minimum wage in UK waters.     
OL,15,FP&O Ferries prompted outrage when it   
OL,16,Freplaced staff with agency workers paid
OL,17,Fless than the minimum wage.            
OL,19,FThe prime minister has backed calls for
OL,20,Fthe boss of P&O Ferries to resign.     
